  <p><em>"For both touring and studio work I have found Yamaha keyboards to be the most versatile. The Motif XF series is the highlight of my performance rig."</em></p>
  <p>Adam Sofo is a Sydney based Pianist and Film Composer. Adam currently plays keyboards and programmes for the current world wide hit TV show, The Voice. Adam did a world tour playing keys with the multi-award winning band Silverchair. He has also played keyboards for Australia's top selling artists, most recently Guy Sebastian and currently Axle Whitehead. </p>
  <p>Adam is based at Trackdown Scoring Stage Fox Studios in Sydney where he composes music for film and television. Adam has recently composed music for the feature film 'Short Beach' now showing in cinemas. He played keys on Stephan Elliot's feature film 'A Few Best Men' and is currently composing music for ABC commercial, Screentime Australia and Trackdown Scoring Stage.</p>
  <p>Adam is highly regarded as a live performer, arranger, programmer and composer for film and television.</p>
